{"title":"四川人，起来！","authors":["高奇"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":10,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"四川人，起来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四川人，起来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象保路同志会"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"围攻成都府那样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九府十三州，一百单八县，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全四川省的老百姓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一齐起来！起来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿着锄头起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿着梭标（蛇矛）起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿着板刀起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿着菜刀起来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛耳炮也好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸟枪也好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吊刀子，剪刀，锥针，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么都好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一齐拿到手里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"起来！起来！起来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨天是活捉赵尔丰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天是活捉蒋介石。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把这个残民以逞的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万恶滔天的卖国贼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快给大家活捉着！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要让他跑掉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但也不要把他杀掉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等候全国人民的公判！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他有飞机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要让他飞上天！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把那飞机的翅膀摘掉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把飞机场封锁起来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞机是美国人造的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞机场是四川人造的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四川人有权"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"占领飞机场！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他有特务，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要让他们横行无忌！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把他们抓起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"强迫他们劳动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让他们改过自新。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要不服从，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打断他们的狗腿！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒋介石只是一个人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四川人是七千万个。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难道七千万个就只等于一串零，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连一个也不如了吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么让这卖国贼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在四川省的空中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自由自在的飞来飞去？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么让这卖国贼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火烧了重庆城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又自由自在地飞往成都，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一屁股坐在四川人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七千万个的头上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自由自在的在那儿放屁？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难道四川人真个是“耗子”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"强盗进了仓，大偷大抢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家都躲进洞子里去了？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难道四川人是一群阿斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曹操赶到，生命都难保，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却还在赵云的怀里睡觉？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么可耻呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快把那长江，泯江，沱江，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金沙江，嘉陵江，大渡河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把所有四川的江水河水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"通同挑起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把蒋介石所污秽过的地方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"通同洗干净吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把重庆洗干净，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把成都洗干净，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把峨嵋山洗干净，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把青城山洗干净，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要再让那"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"死心塌地把祖国大拍卖的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"癞皮走狗的洋骚臭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再要臭气逼天！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"起来，大家一齐起来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全中国都快要解放了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打破“天下已治蜀后治”的老例，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让四川先治起来吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让每个四川人都成为朱德，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成为刘伯承，陈毅，聂荣臻吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天有一件大功劳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在等待着四川人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而且是轻而易举的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是登天，不是跨海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而是活捉蒋介石！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"起来，四川人！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九府十三州，一百单八县，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全省的老百姓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一齐起来！起来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活捉蒋介石！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活捉蒋介石！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活捉蒋介石！ 　　　　　　　（九月二十四日）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}